00:21:03.000 --> 00:21:04.680 align:middle line:84%
how they would have
coped with that,

00:21:04.680 --> 00:21:06.510 align:middle line:84%
and then as you
get into adulthood,

00:21:06.510 --> 00:21:08.490 align:middle line:84%
how do you start
to heal or unravel

00:21:08.490 --> 00:21:11.760 align:middle line:84%
some of the trauma that could
have happened in that time

00:21:11.760 --> 00:21:14.550 align:middle line:84%
